non_residential_details.development_type: Change of Use with Extension(s) over 999sqm

description: Mixed use refurbishment, conversion and redevelopment including the retention and change of use of the existing building along with alterations to the external appearance of the building, extensions to the existing building involving an eight storey block adj to railway incorporating communal roof garden, two storey light weight addition to the roof and an additional car parking deck adj to railway development. Will comprise twenty two studio units, sixty 1-bedroomed and eighty six 2-bedroomed self contained flats and six self contained duplex units (including 56 affordable units). The ground floor comprising 2083 sq metres of floorspace for uses falling within Classes A1-A5, D1 and D2 and B1 of the Town and Country Planning (use classes) Order 1987 (as amended) including 637 sq metres of office space together with a total of 124 car parking spaces, 254 cycle spaces, service and amenity facilities
